Adam!

33
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:09,360
Adam!

34
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:17,000
Adam!

35
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:20,320
Adam!

36
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:24,120
Adam!

37
00:14:40,360 --> 00:14:45,040
Adam! Come, return!

38
00:14:47,800 --> 00:14:51,040
Stand! Come home!

39
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:04,080
Adam!

40
00:15:19,640 --> 00:15:23,440
Adam! Adam dear!

41
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:27,800
Mom, wipe your mouth!

42
00:16:18,920 --> 00:16:23,920
Brok, come home!

43
00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:51,240
What a misery!

44
00:16:55,040 --> 00:16:58,200
Damn the stuff.

45
00:16:58,280 --> 00:17:01,520
Shit, how can I drive this?

46
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:05,200
Don't stare and give the stick inside!

47
00:17:36,800 --> 00:17:42,600
We need a fourth!

48
00:17:44,200 --> 00:17:48,880
Not you! You wouldn't keep it.
