49
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:11,600
My condolence.

50
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:19,120
My condolence.

51
00:20:49,200 --> 00:20:51,400
Don't be affraid, little one!

52
00:20:51,480 --> 00:20:53,640
Tell me something!

53
00:20:53,720 --> 00:20:57,880
Mom, what are you two talking about?
It wants us to let her go to its mom.

54
00:20:57,960 --> 00:21:01,160
Shall we? Yes!

55
00:23:21,200 --> 00:23:23,240
Mr. Adam.

56
00:23:27,000 --> 00:23:28,840
Can you hear?

57
00:23:32,880 --> 00:23:35,440
Mr. Adam, open!

58
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:39,840
