Just like an orangutang.

67
00:25:01,360 --> 00:25:03,800
I'm not that bad, mr. Adam.

68
00:25:04,520 --> 00:25:09,280
If I were such bitch as you think,
I would go somewhere where is less work.

69
00:25:09,760 --> 00:25:17,120
I can work!
You and work? You can do discgrace at most.

70
00:25:17,760 --> 00:25:23,880
